      <title>全球军备开支飙升 以色列国防出口创历史新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/israeli-defense-exports-hit-record-as-global-arms-spending-soars</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于乌克兰和加沙等地区的战争引发全球军备竞赛的担忧，去年以色列的国防出口创下了历史新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/israeli-defense-exports-hit-record-as-global-arms-spending-soars</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 12:53:13 GMT</pubDate>
