    <item>
      <title>乌克兰战争陷入停滞 普京将访问朝鲜和越南</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/putin-to-visit-north-korea-vietnam-as-his-war-in-ukraine-stalls</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京将访问朝鲜和越南，这是他罕见的长期合作伙伴，因为他在乌克兰战争中面临新的挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/putin-to-visit-north-korea-vietnam-as-his-war-in-ukraine-stalls</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 11:20:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国特使访问以色列试图平息与真主党的局势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/us-envoy-flies-to-israel-in-bid-to-prevent-war-with-hezbollah</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国外交官阿莫斯·霍克斯坦前往中东，试图缓解以色列和真主党之间的紧张局势，这种紧张局势有可能升级为一场跨越黎巴嫩边境的全面战争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/us-envoy-flies-to-israel-in-bid-to-prevent-war-with-hezbollah</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 10:02:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>降低药品成本需要的不仅仅是美国的议价能力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/drug-price-cuts-will-require-more-than-us-government-authority</link>
      <description><![CDATA[政府的新权力仅限于医疗保险购买的 10 种药品，在谈判开始前，制造商可能会在几年内收取更高的价格。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/drug-price-cuts-will-require-more-than-us-government-authority</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 10:00:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>民意调查显示，英国改革党支持率保持创纪录水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/bloomberg-uk-poll-of-polls-reform-stays-at-record-levels</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在周一发布竞选宣言之前，奈杰尔·法拉奇领导的英国改革党在彭博民意调查中保持了创纪录的支持率，而领先的工党和里希·苏纳克领导的执政保守党的支持率在最近几天均略有下滑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/bloomberg-uk-poll-of-polls-reform-stays-at-record-levels</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据美联社报道，以色列官员称内塔尼亚胡已解散战争内阁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-06-17/urgent-israeli-officials-say-netanyahu-has-dissolved-the-war-cabinet-after-key-partner-bolted-government</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列特拉维夫（美联社）——以色列官员周一表示，以色列总理本雅明内塔尼亚胡解散了负责指挥加沙战争的具有影响力的战时内阁，此前几天，该内阁的一名关键成员因对以色列领导人处理战争的方式感到不满而逃离政府。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-06-17/urgent-israeli-officials-say-netanyahu-has-dissolved-the-war-cabinet-after-key-partner-bolted-government</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 09:29:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度火车相撞至少造成 8 人死亡，数十人受伤</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-06-17/urgent-trains-collide-in-eastern-india-killing-at-least-5-with-rescue-work-ongoing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新德里（美联社）——官员称，周一，一列货运列车与一列客运列车在印度东部西孟加拉邦相撞，造成至少 9 人死亡，数十人受伤。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-06-17/urgent-trains-collide-in-eastern-india-killing-at-least-5-with-rescue-work-ongoing</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 05:32:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国指责菲律宾船只在南海与中国船只相撞</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-06-17/urgent-china-says-a-chinese-vessel-and-philippine-supply-ship-collided-in-the-disputed-south-china-sea</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台北（美联社）——中国海岸警卫队称，一艘中国船只与一艘菲律宾补给船于周一在南海有争议的斯普拉特利群岛附近发生碰撞，这是领土争端不断升级的最新一次爆发，​​引发了人们的警惕。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-06-17/urgent-china-says-a-chinese-vessel-and-philippine-supply-ship-collided-in-the-disputed-south-china-sea</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 03:17:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>针对勒庞极右翼的保障措施开始瓦解</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-16/french-election-safeguards-against-le-pen-s-far-right-are-starting-to-unravel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在法国立法选举之前，阻止民族主义团体掌权的传统规范正在瓦解，国民联盟党极右翼领导人玛丽娜·勒庞 (Marine Le Pen) 意外地获得了新的支持者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-16/french-election-safeguards-against-le-pen-s-far-right-are-starting-to-unravel</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
